{"tid":2390034,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Elon Musk在廣播表示自己是bitcoin支持者 比特幣價格一度拉漲600美元","createTime":"2021-02-01T09:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T03:50:59.000Z","uid":295230,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"589c9283c3e9dd3d06f810d54ae8c18ac09a58f1","tid":2390034,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T09:46:50.000Z","msg":"特斯拉CEO Elon Musk在接受美國社交媒體Clubhouse訪談時表示：&ldquo;比特幣是一件好事，所以，我是比特幣的支持者。&rdquo;馬斯克稱自己曾於2013年在比特幣交易中分得一杯羹，他的許多朋友多年來一直試圖說服他買賣比特幣。他還說至少應該在8年前購買比特幣，並承認自己在比特幣交易的盛宴中來遲。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">在馬斯克發表此番言論之後，比特幣價格一度拉漲600美元。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n馬斯克認為，在傳統金融領域，比特幣真的快要被廣泛接受。<br />\n<br />\n此前，馬斯克經常拿狗狗幣（Dogecoin，用戶數僅次於比特幣的第二大虛擬貨幣）開玩笑，但他表示其實這只是開玩笑而已。 &ldquo;最具諷刺意味的現像是，狗狗幣將在未來成為地球的貨幣。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是，上週五，馬斯克在推特上更改簡介為&ldquo;#bitcoin&rdquo;（比特幣）後，比特幣立即飆升至38000美元以上，一度大漲18%，創近兩週以來高點。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，一直以來馬斯克經常在推特上發布狗狗幣或比特幣有關的消息，這也常常導致這些虛擬加密貨幣價格隨之飆升。<br />\n<br />\n今年1月8日，《比特幣億萬富豪》的作者本&middot;梅茲里奇（Ben Mezrich）發布推特稱：&ldquo;我再也不會拒絕接受比特幣支付。&rdquo;隨後，馬斯克在推特上回復稱：&ldquo;我也不會拒絕。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n更早前，馬斯克還曾表示過比特幣結構非常出色，相較於央行發行的貨幣，虛擬貨幣更加可靠。他也曾透露過自己只持有0.25個比特幣，還是朋友多年前贈送而來。"},{"pid":"b0afe79200a00a4a5420669d1eeb04796b82467b","tid":2390034,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:38:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ad5731512e2918b2a4d2d07a3bf0928734a76ee","tid":2390034,"uid":142678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:40:15.000Z","msg":"600都好講"},{"pid":"f639d14ea8ae1fb64b8000a8fe5d865402473611","tid":2390034,"uid":384590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:41:41.000Z","msg":"Bitcoin is the future gold"},{"pid":"b0b6a0cbb8969228316309cc9d9ab240d8ac8b3d","tid":2390034,"uid":40309,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T10:44:57.000Z","msg":"600?, 咁都入佢數痴撚線, BTC 日日波幅都唔止600啦<br />\n 無6萬都唔好報啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"2a2971cfdd365881535e3da0becc1b316ca5c91d","tid":2390034,"uid":218158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T11:02:18.000Z","msg":"monero"},{"pid":"fcb70fb6fd37e9e71a87a5bd04ada4ec7b4d4dd1","tid":2390034,"uid":230043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T11:17:01.000Z","msg":"Elon 爸爸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c79f5667b90198f78826afa16e168cb8a4a3bdb4","tid":2390034,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:40:42.000Z","msg":"連登仔：騙局"},{"pid":"48c01dd4bd08e66e72523dbb88921256191e17d4","tid":2390034,"uid":1484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:42:57.000Z","msg":"幾分鐘爆3000點 之後一日回返晒 個個走晒去炒細coin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d300208f53cf7d23a1b666331b9d2eea27f77998","tid":2390034,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:46:37.000Z","msg":"搵人塞住佢把口啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf6759ed82d057fe8d43507999dadd0d51fc0e6","tid":2390034,"uid":352160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:47:40.000Z","msg":"600<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTC一日上落成皮，600 WFC"},{"pid":"4fb9c33ffccadb20b5396c86479ade04f233dc4e","tid":2390034,"uid":87123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:47:58.000Z","msg":"又出口術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb93d322c2e25c722cd53d4bacbc22b1c26dd6b","tid":2390034,"uid":43369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T03:48:40.000Z","msg":"elon papa點石成金"},{"pid":"18737444627c3898